Voidface web demo — scaffold placeholder.

The web demo is a static Vite + TypeScript app that loads the ONNX
generator through `onnxruntime-web` with the WebGPU execution provider,
runs entirely client-side (files never leave the tab), and offers a
drag-and-drop UI.

This directory is intentionally empty until Phase R5. See
`../../Documentation/deployment/onnx.md` for the export path and
`../../Documentation/architecture.md` for the shape of the release.
